cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with cross-modal retrieval systems, which involve both computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) are the most likely sub-categories. Additionally, since the proposed system is based on deep neural networks, cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) are also likely sub-categories.
